[00:00.43]	[London. The Parliament-house.,]
[00:01.31]	[Flourish. Enter KING HENRY VI, EXETER, GLOUCESTER,
[00:01.74]	+ WARWICK, SOMERSET, and SUFFOLK; the BISHOP OF
[00:02.18]	+ WINCHESTER, RICHARD PLANTAGENET, and others.
